title: USC's Nunez to miss LSU game
text: USC's Nunez to miss LSU game With the quarterback unable to throw because of a bruised shoulder, USC to go with Orth Post to Facebook USC's Nunez to miss LSU game With the quarterback unable to throw because of a bruised shoulder, USC to go with Orth Check out this story on greenvilleonline.com: http://grnol.co/1LkFZgh Cancel Send A link has been sent to your friend's email address.
